title: Jennifer Lawrence drops The Rosie Project for Darren Aronofsky’s next indie film?
text:
Jennifer Lawrence drops The Rosie Project for Darren Aronofsky’s next indie film? 
Published By: TotalFilm.com - Today 
Jennifer Lawrence is in line for Darren Aronofsky’s next film, but has dropped out of Richard Linklater's adaptation of The Rosie Project....
